title: #92Noon! Spielman/Leber/Wobby
description: OTAs are underway and PA is live from the TCO Performance Center in Eagan! Vikings GM Rick Spielman stops by to talk about how the Vikings practices are going, Ben Leber is in studio to discuss the latest news on the NFL, and Wobby talks colonoscopy, football, and other sports!
